name: A VOID KEY
description:
Submission for the Mini Jam 67:Void.

There are 8 levels.

Controls:

Arrow Key/WASD - Restart Level - Main Menu

Goal:

Get all the keys to open chests.

Tip:

When a portal appear it can be used to control the remaining keys.
